Specialist Joseph Urbanczyk was drafted into the @USarmy in 1968 & deployed to Vietnam with Company C, 321 Infantry of the 196th Light Infantry. Sadly he was KIA by enemy forces on Mar. 13, 1969.

Technical Sgt. John Jenkins grew up in East Buffalo & was drafted into the @USArmy in 1967. He served in Vietnam with the 11th Infantry in the 5th Infantry Division leading his own firing squad.
